{"tid":806454,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"地震波","createTime":"2018-09-04T16:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T17:41:35.000Z","uid":197125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6248516ab6d6153e70e51adbdc3d7940c059489","tid":806454,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"地震波有分P波（縱波）同S波（橫波）兩種，地震發生時，P波會走得比較快而S波較慢，但係點解就算離震央比較遠時，我地感受到嘅S波同時有縱向同橫向呢？Thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c91e83cb9a85aeab63a7b306312e056164c48f","tid":806454,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"666"},{"pid":"89689f2f169afff03a548eb77d0513558691edbd","tid":806454,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"你點知你感受緊咩波"},{"pid":"bfa7322913d6545bd4a695db50d32546e2d3400f","tid":806454,"uid":117251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"Alexandra Daddario"},{"pid":"6fb99cd17794c7a267f1afd23a006dc3dad02be4","tid":806454,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89689f2f169afff03a548eb77d0513558691edbd","tid":806454,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"你點知你感受緊咩波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:04:37.000Z","msg":"點會唔知？就算當你冇感覺，儀器都record到有縱有橫嫁"},{"pid":"643147ada73faddb44eca69104aa7cebd932066d","tid":806454,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:30:22.000Z","msg":"縱波同橫波入面個縱字同橫字唔係講震既方向<br />\n你睇下wiki先"},{"pid":"66d378b7859e9e5de945ea365f14ce399a4dca10","tid":806454,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"643147ada73faddb44eca69104aa7cebd932066d","tid":806454,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:30:22.000Z","msg":"縱波同橫波入面個縱字同橫字唔係講震既方向<br />\n你睇下wiki先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"P波：P代表主要（Primary）或壓縮（Pressure），為一種縱波，粒子振動方向和波前進方平行，在所有地震波中，前進速度最快，也最早抵達。<br />\nS波：S意指次要（Secondary）或剪力（Shear），前進速度僅次於P波，粒子振動方向垂直於波的前進方向，是一種橫波。"}]}